---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Explore the future of our crypto project with this detailed roadmap. Track our key milestones and major developments, from the initial launch to long-term goals."
  title="Project Roadmap Â· Crypto Project"
>
  <section class="py-8 px-4 mx-auto max-w-7xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-6">Project Roadmap</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-center mb-12 text-gray-600">
      This roadmap outlines the major milestones of Aaron Network, highlighting key achievements and future goals.
    </p>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Completed milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2l4-4m6 2a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-green-500">June-July 2024</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Airdrop for community</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Current milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-orange-500 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-green-500 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2l4-4m6 2a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-orange-500">August-September 2024</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Development of a browser, a dashboard for the network and functionality for calculating the address scoring</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6 1a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-400">October 2024</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Preparing for network launch</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6 1a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-400">November 2024</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Network launch</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6 1a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-400">December 2024</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Development of a frontend for conducting voting</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6 1a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-400">January 2025</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Development of user profiles</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Future milestone -->
      <div class="flex items-start border-l-4 border-gray-400 pl-6">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-gray-400 mr-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6 1a9 9 0 1 1-18 0a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z" /></svg>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-400">February 2025</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700">Development of public messaging functionality</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
